osed sets of parameters for both denatured and\nleft-handed DNA forms. Altogether, our work paves the way for a scalable\nquantitative model of bacterial DNA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Apr 2019 16:51:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-26"}
