ons, and try to define a minimum standard for acceptable level\nof information when reporting the results of statistical procedures in High\nEnergy Physics publications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Apr 2019 08:44:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2020 07:22:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-17"}
