ithms investigated in this work will be made publicly\navailable as part of the open-source software platform Medical Imaging\nInteraction Toolkit (MITK).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Apr 2019 12:47:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-29"}
