ason for the quenching of the\nBGG. Future large-field photometric surveys, such as Euclid and LSST, will be\nable to confirm and extend these results by probing a wider mass range and a\nlarger variety of environment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Apr 2019 14:16:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
