ons, and iv) $\\simeq$ 3.5 times\nstronger flux-centroid correlation coefficient than the original analysis.\nThese points could be explained by larger systematics in their reduction,\npotentially impacting their conclusions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Apr 2019 15:26:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Feb 2020 18:35:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-18"}
